name: CryptoMushrooms #002 - Macrolepiota Procera
description:
This spectacularly large and pale brownish mushroom is also know as “Parasol Mushroom”. It grows solitary, scattered, or clustered on the soil, in open grassy places and in mixed woods. Globally it is widespread in temperate regions. These mushrooms are popularly sauteed in melted butter, but is also edible raw.
